text: Hedong Subdistrict () is a subdistrict in Chengzhong District, Liuzhou, Guangxi, China. , it has 5 residential communities and 2 villages under its administration. == See also == * List of township-level divisions of Guangxi == References == Category:Township-level divisions of Guangxi Category:Liuzhou
